events.name: Weekly Labs
events.description:
ShockSoc's regular Lab sessions.
Bring your own stuff to work on, pick up one of our projects, or start work on something new.
Our lab sessions are open to everyone.

events.name: Graduate Careers with MI5, SIS, & GCHQ
events.description:
Come and join us for this insight event, where the organisations will be sharing a presentation about what it is like to work for them, their missions, and the routes avaliable.
Please note the speakers will be virtual and if you'll be coming, try and let us know before-hand through the form.
